1. INSTALLATION
Just copy the folder bluenatic to themes/ inside your WackoWiki
installation. You are now able to choose the bluenatic theme from your
settings menu. Enjoy!


2. THANK YOU
Gururaj for his open web template called NoProps I used as a basic
template for this theme.
> http://openwebdesign.org/userinfo.phtml?user=kpgururaja

All the guys of the tango project for their wonderful icons I used
in the QuickAction container.
> http://www.tango-project.org

TheBone for his help in developing this theme and sharing his
webspace.

Martin aka SkipPer for his beta-testing and great ideas for Bluenatic.

The whole open source community for their work!


